0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:26:37.000Z","msg":"Fb"},{"pid":"3e84cc4cd110bcf90392a2e91962931c02c83e28","tid":1657114,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:27:42.000Z","msg":"面書呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2813006ff98dd1e2edc87c213fff376f997fc109","tid":1657114,"uid":156018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:31:40.000Z","msg":"點解今日啲「冇人講」標題既post永遠都係連樓主都唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76d613d51bd6cd7928e6b98225941feff7ab836","tid":1657114,"uid":270374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:32:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英、德、日、台版人權法案</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以海外活動來說，300萬不算多，大家考慮下。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=79f47513\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/</a><br />\n<br />\n新一階段工作為期兩年，除繼續經營美國網絡外，我們亦將集中德國、英國、日本、台灣等四大重點國家，拓展我們的連結及遊說網絡，當中德國是過去多次就人權問題發聲的歐盟成員國之一、英國是《中英聯合聲明》簽署國、台灣則同樣是威權中國下的命運共同體，而日本乃東亞最具軟實力、近年相當關注中國影響的國家。<br />\n<br />\n新一階段國際遊說工作為期兩年，眾籌金額300萬，包括：<br />\n【海外網絡】資助海外港人進行遊說，在重點國家建立長期遊說網絡（約50萬）<br />\n【主動外訪】針對外國國會及政府機關，主動出擊進行策略性外訪（約100萬）【🔎訪港考察】邀請議員及社運組織來港考察，壯大香港與其他公民社會（約50萬）<br />\n【研究團隊】聘請本地研究團隊，為遊說及倡議工作提供法律研究和研究支援（約100萬）"},{"pid":"f26e8011f1464f817aba08118ec049fb01ec5771","tid":1657114,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:33:07.000Z","msg":"佢係直接post定點<br />\nShare同自己開po講已經有分別"},{"pid":"cd90af3122ac12cb4132c70aad4b670600562454","tid":1657114,"uid":69221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:44:41.000Z","msg":"樓主死左老母冇人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bebd2d7463bb837c758eb869ef279a110b4c673","tid":1657114,"uid":240960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2be988249e26cfa388765bdca7e40eb4f670e47","tid":1657114,"uid":210895,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:12:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:51:36.000Z","msg":"邊撚度有連登兩個字"},{"pid":"39481f881e25435b14f1087f9453f23490635ea7","tid":1657114,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T04:55:34.000Z","msg":"點解唔拉羅范椒芬？"},{"pid":"bdec1cca97e8abef270bfe2d4a47bfb897bd58c5","tid":1657114,"uid":241878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:07:16.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"86c1780e05d8d41b524a582d0c8b265eb0cbf4fd","tid":1657114,"uid":262125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:20:35.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"866f2c86abb5061ecc2c087d613141b5aba515f0","tid":1657114,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5135eb9836ff36346225b56fa449f0bc82ea4d","tid":1657114,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"沉啦屌你"},{"pid":"22f512f32e0cb98633c7c14ce8e9ba9ff77fd477","tid":165711